{"tid":781930,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【闔家都係狗】 賤朗有咩屋企人？ 全家幅畫像一眼睇晒","createTime":"2018-08-16T09:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T02:56:16.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"927ca4f5ceab00b75a49ac8aaea0d518b744e519","tid":781930,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/08/16/2/22b703898e5d225be6d333be454a343e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F2%2F22b703898e5d225be6d333be454a343e.jpg&h=3d321cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賤朗所有唐氏綜合症家人<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙巨星 C 朗拿度出愛錫家人，日前他就在 Insatgram 上分享一幅全家幅畫像，一次過「曬冷」自己的兄弟姐妹，畫面十分溫馨，最特別的是，這幅畫像出自他姐姐的手筆，別具意義。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/08/16/7/7348e9d18998b3271cef930b322a68d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F7%2F7348e9d18998b3271cef930b322a68d0.jpg&h=626ad408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朗母做雞養大賤朗<br />\n<br />\n這幅巨型全家福畫作由 C 朗拿度的姐姐 Katia 繪製，畫面中的 C 朗拿度分別搭著媽媽 Maria Dolores 和另一個姐姐 Elma 的膊頭，至於 Katia 與大哥 Hugo 則站在另一邊，整個畫面都充滿著愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/08/16/2/21e6a4779ff464aebd66bb3b095c0d27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F2%2F21e6a4779ff464aebd66bb3b095c0d27.jpg&h=2ab2f1b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老母辛苦做雞養大佢<br />\n<br />\n這幅全家幅放置在 C 朗拿度媽媽在巴西開設的餐聽，她過去曾於家鄉開設餐廳，由於生意十分好，決定再下一城，在巴西的 Casa Aveiro 開設另一間餐廳，同樣生意興隆，不知道 C 朗拿度媽媽日後會否考慮在香港開分店呢？"},{"pid":"362524d55da6cac15d117a8651afec59bca7ab2b","tid":781930,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"cd98c78ebb333134c3c572a74651a96ca75f60f0","tid":781930,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"a0f2f3984a25d67497896afddd90cdb561760f1a","tid":781930,"uid":58811,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"Too much la 王騎"},{"pid":"2df5b62c076755d01639cf8f2e93d89ca133d34b","tid":781930,"uid":6717,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"做多左"},{"pid":"b9e7fb2c03e330c83c555ad1093f7dc45d07327c","tid":781930,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"樓主迷朗"},{"pid":"532aa05c56f2bd50725c3100b5267645ee1d5656","tid":781930,"uid":141543,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"其實王騎老母可能先係....."},{"pid":"0d5361d0ce3e2334d35d89b9019bf73db136b493","tid":781930,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"今次一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744c867c46b9c4c29db8e7aee434404c172ff5f3","tid":781930,"uid":34490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"集中反賤種好過啦"},{"pid":"bcb6e5cce68c6bbf8620cd7cae15fb7ea51af6b1","tid":781930,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"把口臭撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955c3d08cc519b2a574cb01ee7ba850f0d7ca357","tid":781930,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"今次唔好笑"},{"pid":"44dc4a38d71c54c971954f8753229268cfdd3f89","tid":781930,"uid":192158,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2612fef0cd674785c05966c1e518fd462c2b9eb","tid":781930,"uid":13975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T00:56:05.000Z","msg":"on9仔 做多左啦"},{"pid":"b1528e19e0d0da9c48ee7de712a8b09b7572